PRODUCT INFORMATION:

  • Double section structure, wall mount.
  •  Stylish and accurate design.
  •  Standard black color.
  •  Optional support feet for floor installation.
  •  Removable side doors with quick opening mechanism allow for easy installation and
    maintaining.
  •  Optional cable entries from top and bottom plate.
  •  Cooling fans.
  •  Withstand a max load of 120.
  •  Material: high quality cold rolled steel.
  •  Thickness: square hole strips 2.0mm,others 1.2mm.
  •  Surface finish: de-grease, acid pickling, rust prevention process, pure water cleaning, static
    electricity plastic painting.
